07:25:50 [Warning] NativeCdpBridge.Application.Services.AgentMessageLogger: << Agent | to:telegram:7382041514 | MAYA API - Part 2/6: Checkout API

POST /checkout/v1/checkouts (PUBLIC key)
Request body:
- totalAmount: {value, currency, details:{discount,serviceCharge,shippingFee,tax,subtotal}}
- buyer: {firstName,middleName,lastName,birthday(YYYY-MM-DD),customerSince,sex(M/F),contact:{phone,email},shippingAddress:{firstName,middleName,lastName,phone,email,line1,line2,city,state,zipCode,countryCode,shippingType(ST/SD)},billingAddress:{line1,line2,city,state,zipCode,countryCode}}
- items: [{name,quantity,code,description,amount:{value,details},totalAmount:{value,details}}]
- redirectUrl: {success,failure,cancel}
- requestReferenceNumber: string
- metadata: object
Response: {checkoutId, redirectUrl}

GET /checkout/v1/checkouts/:checkoutId (SECRET key)
Response: {id,items,requestReferenceNumber,createdAt,updatedAt,expiredAt,paymentScheme,expressCheckout,refundedAmount,canPayPal,status,paymentStatus,paymentDetails:{responses,paymentAt,3ds:bool},buyer,merchant,totalAmount,redirectUrl,transactionReferenceNumber,metadata}

PAYMENT STATUSES: PENDING_TOKEN, PENDING_PAYMENT, FOR_AUTHENTICATION, AUTHENTICATING, AUTH_SUCCESS, AUTH_FAILED, PAYMENT_PROCESSING, PAYMENT_SUCCESS, PAYMENT_FAILED, PAYMENT_EXPIRED(1hr from creation/15min from auth), VOIDED, REFUNDED

CHECKOUT WEBHOOKS:
CHECKOUT_SUCCESS -> PAYMENT_SUCCESS
CHECKOUT_FAILURE -> PAYMENT_FAILED
CHECKOUT_DROPOUT -> PAYMENT_EXPIRED
Body = Get Checkout response. Retries: now, +5m, +15m, +45m
07:26:03 [Warning] NativeCdpBridge.Application.Services.AgentMessageLogger: << Agent | to:telegram:7382041514 | MAYA API - Part 3/6: Payment Vault + Customer + Subscriptions

PAYMENT TOKENS:
POST /payments/v1/payment-tokens (PUBLIC)
Body: {card:{number,expMonth,expYear,cvc}}
Token states: AVAILABLE, CURRENTLY_IN_USE, USED, EXPIRED, PREVERIFICATION, VERIFYING, VERIFICATION_FAILED

PAYMENTS:
POST /payments/v1/payments (SECRET)
Body: {paymentTokenId,totalAmount:{amount,currency},buyer:{firstName,lastName,contact:{phone},billingAddress:{...}},redirectUrl:{success,failure,cancel}}
GET /payments/v1/payments/:id (SECRET)
GET /payments/v1/payment-rrns/:rrn (SECRET)

CUSTOMERS:
POST /payments/v1/customers (SECRET) - {firstName(req),middleName,lastName(req),birthday(YYYY-MM-DD),sex,contact:{phone,email},billingAddress:{line1,line2,city,state,zipCode,countryCode},metadata}
GET/PUT/DELETE /payments/v1/customers/:id (SECRET)

CARDS:
POST /payments/v1/customers/:id/cards (SECRET) - {paymentTokenId(req),isDefault:bool,redirectUrl:{...}}
GET /payments/v1/customers/:id/cards (SECRET) - list
GET/PUT/DELETE /payments/v1/customers/:id/cards/:cardToken (SECRET)
POST /payments/v1/customers/:id/cards/:cardToken/payments (SECRET) - execute payment

SUBSCRIPTIONS:
POST /payments/v1/customers/:id/cards/:cardToken/subscriptions (SECRET)
Body: {description(req),totalAmount:{amount(req),currency(req)},interval:DAY|MONTH|YEAR(req),intervalCount(req),startDate:YYYY-MM-DD(req)}
GET /payments/v1/customers/:id/cards/:cardToken/subscriptions (SECRET)
GET/DELETE /payments/v1/subscriptions/:id (SECRET)
GET /payments/v1/subscriptions/:id/payments (SECRET)

VAULT WEBHOOKS: 3DS_PAYMENT_SUCCESS, 3DS_PAYMENT_FAILURE, 3DS_PAYMENT_DROPOUT, RECURRING_PAYMENT_SUCCESS, RECURRING_PAYMENT_FAILURE
